{"tid":867823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首關於屋企人嘅歌","createTime":"2018-10-19T03:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T09:00:13.000Z","uid":212314,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"98f8146b0c163a9110f42b85dec0cf1f210fdc9a","tid":867823,"uid":212314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"一人一首聽完好想衝返屋企攬住屋企人嘅歌<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ViqNhuXgROc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FViqNhuXgROc&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fa38849c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ViqNhuXgROc</a><br />\n<br />\n小肥首負親真係次次聽都好心up 啲詞真係填得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曾經收起的抱擁<br />\n曾經懶去寄的書信<br />\n留到葬禮那一刻已是無用<br />\n墓碑的旁邊 我即使向你談論今天的瑣碎<br />\n你都不覆半句<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家真係要好好珍惜身邊嘅屋企人<br />\n多啲表達自己嘅愛意 唔好等失去左先後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3790bdb558e1c644a0f9d10bf7445049790141dd","tid":867823,"uid":140580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:56:32.000Z","msg":"早點回家"},{"pid":"13752dbd189a8d6c1df8bc6d4c44b38b7086dd24","tid":867823,"uid":126690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16baec9f6c5227ae708f3ece8c690150d616a93b","tid":867823,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"絕對"},{"pid":"3a323bacb382eafeb7cd5374e3427235aff9d28f","tid":867823,"uid":55280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"李克勤 - 失魂記<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qHQ5QcqhsnQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqHQ5QcqhsnQ&d=wwoenDbXDu%2FeL7ZuvUSpHaWGW%2FHqnCn